                     <interp inst="t18130407-9-off45" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18130407-9-cd46" type="crimeDate">24th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130407-9-off45 t18130407-9-cd46"></join>, a mantle, value 30 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18130407-9-victim100" type="victimName">
                        Joshua 
                        Griffen
                     <interp inst="t18130407-9-victim100" type="surname" value="Griffen"></interp>
